  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted to investigate the therapeutic efficacy and safety of transcranial
      direct current stimulation (tDCS) over the primary motor cortex of patients with acute
      migraine attack.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
